title: Project Planning and Requirements Gathering
description: Define project scope, objectives, and requirements. Gather input from subject matter experts and stakeholders.

title: Data Acquisition and Preprocessing
description: Identify and acquire relevant seismic data sources. Preprocess data for machine learning model training.

title: Machine Learning Model Development
description: Research and develop advanced machine learning algorithms for seismic data interpretation.

title: Model Training and Evaluation
description: Train and evaluate the developed machine learning models using the preprocessed seismic data.

title: User Interface and Visualization
description: Design and develop a user-friendly interface for interpreting seismic data using the trained models.

title: Testing and Quality Assurance
description: Develop comprehensive test plans and perform thorough testing of the application and models.

title: Deployment and Monitoring
description: Deploy the application to production environments and implement monitoring and logging systems.

title: Documentation and User Training
description: Develop comprehensive documentation and provide training for end-users on using the application.

title: Security and Compliance
description: Ensure the application and data handling processes comply with relevant security and regulatory requirements.
